service.name: Community Development Employment Projects Participant Supplement
service.description: The Community Development Employment Project Participant Supplement (CPS) is an additional payment made to eligible CDEP wages participants. Community Development Employment Projects (CDEP) wages participants receive CDEP wages for their participation in the Remote Jobs and Communities Programme (RJCP).
